---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Snake minimalist Game - Terms and Conditions"
  description="Terms and conditions for Snake minimalist Game published on Google Play Store."
>
  <article class="min-h-screen py-16 space-y-8">
    <header class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#0f1a20]">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Last updated: 22 October 2025</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        These terms govern the use of the mobile application <strong>Snake minimalist Game</strong>
        (the "App"), developed by Andrés Cruz Chipol (the "Developer"). By downloading or using the
        App, you agree to these terms in full.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#5bc0be]">1. Permitted use</h2>
      <p>
        The App is intended solely for personal and recreational use. Commercial use, unauthorized
        distribution, or modification is prohibited without the Developer's express permission.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#5bc0be]">2. Privacy and data</h2>
      <p>
        Snake minimalist Game does not request sensitive personal data. The game may collect anonymous usage
        data (such as scores or session metrics) to improve the experience. Data will not be shared with third
        parties without your explicit consent.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#5bc0be]">3. User-generated content</h2>
      <p>
        Any content or feedback you voluntarily provide may be used by the Developer for improvements or
        promotional materials, while keeping your anonymity.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#5bc0be]">4. Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>
        All elements of the App (including code, graphics, and sounds) are owned by the Developer. You do not
        acquire ownership rights by downloading or using it.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#5bc0be]">5. Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        The App is provided "as is" without express or implied warranties. The Developer is not responsible for
        direct or indirect damages that may arise from using the App.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#5bc0be]">6. Changes to the terms</h2>
      <p>
        The Developer may update these terms at any time. Changes will be communicated through the App listing
        on Google Play Store or within the App.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#5bc0be]">7. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For questions about these terms, email <a class="text-[#f42c04] font-medium" href="mailto:andres@andreschipol.com">andres@andreschipol.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <footer class="pt-6 text-sm text-gray-500">
      <p>Thank you for playing Snake minimalist Game.</p>
    </footer>
  </article>
</Layout>

